name: madbeku a to-do list for figma
description:
"madbeku" is a mini to-do list for Figma, where you can keep track of things you need to do. with "madbeku" no more switching between apps to check your to-do's.


✔ light and dark mode

✔ auto-layout + variants

✔ & more


I hope you'll like it 😍

Share your feedback, Also don't forget to share it with your design ninja's 🥷
